0757			; Create File 
0757			; ----------- 
0757			; 
0757			; With current bank  
0757			; Load Block 0 Config 
0757			; Get max file id number 
0757			; Increment file id number 
0757			; Save Config 
0757			; Find free block 
0757			; Set buffer with file name and file id 
0757			; Write buffer to free block  
0757			 
0757			 
0757			; hl point to file name 
0757			; hl returns file id 
0757			 
0757			; file format: 
0757			; byte 0 - file id 
0757			; byte 1 - extent number 
0757			; byte 2-> data 
