2c5b			; | MONITOR ( -- ) Display system breakpoint/monitor | DONE 
2c5b			; | | At start the current various registers will be displayed with contents. 
2c5b			; | | Top right corner will show the most recent debug marker seen. 
2c5b			; | | The bottom of the screen will also show the values of the data stack pointer (DSP) 
2c5b			; | | and the return stack pointer (RSP). 
2c5b			; | | Pressing: 
2c5b			; | |  
2c5b			; | |    1 - Initial screen 
2c5b			; | |  
2c5b			; | |    2 - Display a data dump of HL 
2c5b			; | |  
2c5b			; | |    3 - Display a data dump of DE 
2c5b			; | |  
2c5b			; | |    4 - Display a data dump of BC 
2c5b			; | |  
2c5b			; | |    5 - Display a data dump of HL 
2c5b			; | |  
2c5b			; | |    6 - Display a data dump of DSP 
2c5b			; | |  
2c5b			; | |    7 - Display a data dump of RSP 
2c5b			; | |  
2c5b			; | |    8 - Display a data dump of what is at DSP 
2c5b			; | |  
